{"word":"χωνεύω","slug":"χωνεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χωνεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <el>χοάνη</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to cast into a mould (</i><el>χόανος</el>), <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>to cast metal: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κεχωνευμένος</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}